---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于 — AI Toolbox">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-extrabold">👋 关于 AI Toolbox</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">AI Toolbox</strong> 是一个聚焦互联网全栈开发链路的 AI 产品导航站。
        我们持续追踪市场上最新最具影响力的 AI 产品，梳理各产品的核心优势与局限性，帮助开发者与产品经理精准选型。
      </p>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold text-text">🎯 我们的使命</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="relative pl-5">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-[7px] h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent" />
            <strong class="text-text">精准分类</strong> — 按全栈链路（对话/IDE/UI/Agent/媒体/搜索/数据/音频）分类，一目了然
          </li>
          <li class="relative pl-5">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-[7px] h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent" />
            <strong class="text-text">客观评测</strong> — 每个产品标注擅长与不擅长，不吹不黑
          </li>
          <li class="relative pl-5">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-[7px] h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent" />
            <strong class="text-text">持续更新</strong> — 跟进 AI 行业最新动态，每月更新
          </li>
          <li class="relative pl-5">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-[7px] h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent" />
            <strong class="text-text">开源共建</strong> — 内容以 MDX 格式存储，欢迎 PR 贡献
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold text-text">🛠 技术栈</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-accent-light">Astro</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-accent-light">MDX</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-accent-light">Tailwind CSS v4</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-accent-light">Vercel</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold text-text">✏️ 如何贡献</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-2 pl-4">
          <li>1. Fork 仓库</li>
          <li>2. 在 <code class="rounded bg-surface-hover px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs">src/content/products/</code> 目录下添加新的 MDX 文件</li>
          <li>3. 按照 frontmatter 规范填写产品信息</li>
          <li>4. 提交 Pull Request</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-sm">
        Built with ❤️ by the AI Toolbox team · 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
